#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:389
msgid ""
"Try to build Python with `make -C cpython`. Fix any build errors. If you "
"modify the Python source in-tree after a failed build, it may be useful to "
"run `make rebuild`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:393
msgid ""
"Try to finish the build with a top-level `make`. Fix compile errors in `src/"
"core` and any link errors. It may be useful to apply [`upgrade_pythoncapi.py "
"--no-compat`](https://github.com/python/pythoncapi-compat/blob/main/"
"upgrade_pythoncapi.py) to the C extension in `src/core`."
