#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:398
msgid ""
"The file most tightly coupled to the CPython version is `src/core/"
"stack_switching/pystate.c`. Consult the [greenlet TPythonState.cpp](https://"
"github.com/python-greenlet/greenlet/blob/master/src/greenlet/TPythonState."
