msgid "3. Release a new Pyodide alpha version"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:435
msgid ""
"After all the changes are merged, release a new Pyodide alpha version so "
"that people can build packages with the new ABI."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:438
msgid "4. Update packages and release new package set"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:440
msgid ""
"TODO: Update the process after [PEP 783](https://peps.python.org/pep-0783/) "
"is accepted."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../development/maintainers.md:442
msgid ""
"Go to [pyodide/pyodide-recipes](https://github.com/pyodide/pyodide-recipes) "
